Robert Penny, 83, of Malvern East, has been charged with two counts of murder .
He is accused of murdering Claire Acocks and his wife Margaret Penny at Old London Coiffure Hairdressers in 1991 .
Penny was not required to speak during the hearing that lasted less than five minutes .
His current wife was in court today, and the accused is expected to apply for bail on July 6 .